{{Infobox company 
| name   = Camfil. 
| type   = [[Aktiebolag]] 100 % private ownership 
| foundation     = Company founded 1963 in [[Trosa]] by Gösta Larson under the name Camfil AB
| location       = Camfil AB, [[Stockholm]], [[Sweden]], phone +46 (0)8 545 125 00
